{"tid":1027692,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇黎大灣區有機會促成廣東獨立","createTime":"2019-02-19T03:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T16:08:27.000Z","uid":40629,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de77f8d5bcaa8ecfbb32cba86786336aca07e122","tid":1027692,"uid":40629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"香港廣州上海之所以會出現獨立思想<br />\n除左傳統文化被中共多方面破壞加入侵呢個表因外<br />\n其實重有一個原因 就係三地經濟特別發達<br />\n正因為有錢 有錢先會多人黎搵食<br />\n多人黎搵食先會搞亂秩序<br />\n好似香港而家咁 遊客數量不勝負荷<br />\n呢班人成日話香港要靠大陸<br />\n但留意返呢班人本來就冇乜經濟價值<br />\n三地都處於同一個局面 不能管制 坐以待斃<br />\n導致大量蝗蟲 破壞三個地方<br />\n呢三個地方只係小小縮影<br />\n不過都係未來大灣區既景象"},{"pid":"bf38426a07e6fd98a9f297780b95747d9d7d9b20","tid":1027692,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"上海又關大灣區咩事"},{"pid":"6889e21718bce3f436ee6618c3e49018e42c9670","tid":1027692,"uid":40629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf38426a07e6fd98a9f297780b95747d9d7d9b20","tid":1027692,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"上海又關大灣區咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"小小引申返 上海點解都有獨立思想姐"},{"pid":"da72e2c5d60b1e36b24f4c1bf12cefa8ff661427","tid":1027692,"uid":210794,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"我支持廣東獨立<br />\n但香港還香港廣東還廣東"},{"pid":"ddafb0e2ef8d147528713ed8474afc5eaa3f19dc","tid":1027692,"uid":210682,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bf38426a07e6fd98a9f297780b95747d9d7d9b20","tid":1027692,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"上海又關大灣區咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"好明顯樓主係舉例子啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1b312f73ba43efcb56b47c904d8d623cb7bad6","tid":1027692,"uid":40629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da72e2c5d60b1e36b24f4c1bf12cefa8ff661427","tid":1027692,"uid"